window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Athena Hamilton arrived in Vegas with empty pockets and a heart full of hope. Fifteen years later, her pockets are still empty and hope is a four-letter word no longer in her vocabulary.</p> <p>Seduced by a gentleman she thought was her dream come true, she lives in an inescapable nightmare. Now after 15 years, she’s living on borrowed time. All it takes is one mistake too many, and she’ll disappear like so many others she’s known before.</p> <p>A chance meeting with a childhood friend seems to provide the way out she’s been desperate to find. However, she soon discovers that all is not what it seems. Freedom is only an illusion, but hope might be found in the most unlikely place.</p>"; 
